Gcheck v2.0 - Install [Gmail Notification]


Description :
Gmail notification for linux desktop


Dependencies :
1. sleep
2. curl
3. zenity
4. sox


Check dependencies :
1. chmod +x install.sh
2. sudo ./install.sh -c


Install Gcheck v2.0 :
1. chmod +x install.sh
2. sudo ./install.sh -i


Install sox :
1. sudo apt-get install sox libsox-fmt-all


Tested Gcheck on :
1. LMDE2 mate desktop - 3.16.0-4-amd64
2. chromixium 1.5 - 3.13.0-66-generic


Notes :
1. When Gcheck.sh is created, start up this file in your system
